    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute marimo take down waves of invading alien species in this side-scrolling shooter!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >● Overview ●</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 2.5D shooting game that blends classic side-scrolling action with strategic depth-based combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use lock-on shots that can track up to six enemies at once,<br>and powerful charge shots that pierce through both enemies and bullets to wipe out entire swarms!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chain together multi-enemy takedowns to boost your score with an exhilarating combo-based scoring system.<br>Target priority and strategy are the keys to achieving high scores!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >● Features ●</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple controls: move + only two buttons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.5D side-scrolling battles with depth-based gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 stages plus a hidden stage</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Four difficulty levels for beginners to hardcore players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tutorial and full key configuration support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tense orchestral soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bonus in-game database to learn about real-world invasive species</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >● Story ●</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Year 2222.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Environmental destruction has connected the seas and lakes, collapsing freshwater ecosystems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mysterious particles raining down into the water trigger sudden mutations, giving rise to aggressive invasive species.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lake Akan is no exception. Native lifeforms are devoured, and the marimo are pushed to the brink of extinction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >…But then, a single mutated marimo awakens.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wielding a new power to control oxygen through photosynthesis, the tiny sphere rises to fight back against the invaders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To protect its friends, it begins to roll into battle…</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >● Disclaimer ●</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a work of fiction.<br>While some creatures are inspired by real species, their behaviors and ecology may differ from reality.</p>",
